1 0 0 1 54 640 Tm (## What You Are Building) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 626 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 612 Tm (The repo contains two closely related application shapes:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 598 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 584 Tm (- `rag-at-scale`: the baseline RAG demo app without LLM-as-judge enabled) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 570 Tm (- `rag-at-scale-eval`: the eval-enabled app that adds asynchronous judge scoring,) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 556 Tm (  CloudWatch custom metrics, and an eval-specific dashboard) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 542 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 528 Tm (Both apps use the same FastAPI service code and the same ECS Fargate + ALB deployment) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 514 Tm (shape, but they run as separate stacks, services, and images so one can stay stable) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 500 Tm (while the other is used for experiments and evaluation.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 486 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 472 Tm (## Architecture) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 458 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 444 Tm (```mermaid) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 430 Tm (flowchart LR) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 416 Tm (    user[UserBrowserOrAPIClient] --> alb[ApplicationLoadBalancer]) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 402 Tm (    alb --> app[FastAPIService]) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 388 Tm (    app --> retrieval[HybridRetrieval]) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 374 Tm (    retrieval --> reranker[CrossEncoderReranker]) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 360 Tm (    reranker --> answerGen[BedrockAnswerGeneration]) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 346 Tm (    answerGen --> response[UserResponse]) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 332 Tm (    response --> judgeTrigger[AsyncEvalTrigger]) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 318 Tm (    judgeTrigger --> judge[BedrockLLMJudge]) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 304 Tm (    judge --> cwMetrics[CloudWatchCustomMetrics]) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 290 Tm (    judge --> cwLogs[CloudWatchStructuredLogs]) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 276 Tm (    app --> cwInfra[CloudWatchInfraDashboard]) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 262 Tm (    cwMetrics --> cwEval[EvalDashboardWidgets]) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 248 Tm (    cwLogs --> cwEval) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 234 Tm (    docs[\(PDFOrTextCorpus\)] --> app) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 220 Tm (```) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 206 Tm () Tj
