1 0 0 1 54 122 Tm (dependencies.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 108 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 94 Tm (```bash) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 80 Tm (python3.11 -m venv venv) Tj
ET
endstream
