1 0 0 1 54 514 Tm (### Step 5: Build the eval app as a separate image) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 500 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 486 Tm (The eval app uses the same service code but must not replace the baseline app image.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 472 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 458 Tm (For that reason, the repo includes a separate image path:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 444 Tm () Tj
