1 0 0 1 54 346 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 332 Tm (1. start from the already-working baseline production image) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 318 Tm (2. overlay only the updated `src/` tree) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 304 Tm (3. build remotely on native `amd64`) Tj
