1 0 0 1 54 556 Tm (## Safe Operating Rules) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 542 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 528 Tm (To keep demos stable:) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 514 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 500 Tm (1. never update the baseline `rag-at-scale` stack while preparing the eval app) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 486 Tm (2. never push eval builds into the baseline ECR repo) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 472 Tm (3. use separate stack names, service names, dashboards, and metric namespaces) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 458 Tm (4. treat the eval app as disposable and the baseline app as the safe fallback) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 444 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 430 Tm (## Suggested Demo Flow) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 416 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 54 402 Tm (1. Open the baseline app to show the stable production path.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 388 Tm (2. Open the eval app to show the same search experience plus extra observability.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 374 Tm (3. Ingest the `nexus_research_bulletin_2025.pdf` into the eval app.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 360 Tm (4. Ask a fact-rich question.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 346 Tm (5. Show the answer, retrieved chunks, then the eval dashboard and CloudWatch logs.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 332 Tm () Tj
